BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20160122T023000Z
DTEND:20160122T040000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T144146Z
UID:t7ekh8p3qks13pvel0bs34b970@google.com
CREATED:20160120T004009Z
DESCRIPTION:In retail e-commerce\, fast informed decisions are essential to
  creating world-class customer experiences. Chandan Joarder\, Principal Eng
 ineer of Macys.com\, will share lessons learned building a real-time insigh
 t application. He will discuss technical challenges\, how his team solved t
 hem\, and demonstrate what they've built. Their innovative two-pronged appr
 oach to data exploration and visualization incorporates packaged tools like
  Tableau and custom BI dashboards. Please join us at MemSQL HQ in SOMA.\n\n
 Heavy appetizers and drinks will be served. We look forward to seeing you t
 here.\nSCHEDULE:\n\n6:00 - 6:30 Welcome & happy (half) hour\n\n6:30 - 7:15 
 Building Real-Time Digital Insight presentation and demo\n\n7:15 - 8:00 Q&A
  and continued happy hour
LAST-MODIFIED:20160122T025201Z
LOCATION:MemSQL\, 534 4th St\, San Francisco\, CA 94107\, United States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Building Real-Time Digital Insight: MemSQL Talk
TRANSP:OPAQUE
