DESCRIPTION:(415) 292-0101\nBDK Restaurant & Bar is a stylish American tave
 rn located at the The Marker Hotel in San Francisco’s Lower Nob Hill neighb
 orhood.  From dinner with friends and late-night drinks to breakfast meetin
 gs and family weekend brunch\, everyone is treated like a regular at BDK.<b
 r /><br />With the feel of a modern pub in San Francisco\, BDK's inviting s
 etting is highlighted in raw steel\, leather\, polished brass and oak. Our 
 American restaurant menu includes playful touches throughout\, from snacks 
 and starters such as Thai Coconut Red Curry Popcorn and Dungeness Crab Beig
 nets\, to salads like Asparagus + Pea Shoots with sugar snap peas\, mint\, 
 crispy croutons\, ricotta\, and Meyer lemon vinaigrette\, and entrees such 
 as the Pickle Brined Fried Chicken Thighs with coleslaw and mini buttermilk
  biscuits. Dark Chocolate Fudge Cake with salted pretzel crumble and peanut
  butter sauce makes for a decadent finish.<br />
LAST-MODIFIED:20151013T051136Z
LOCATION:501 Geary St.\, San Francisco\, CA 94109
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:BDK
TRANSP:OPAQUE
