BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20150813T220000Z
DTEND:20150813T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T144146Z
UID:nevs9s0neilljrapoq0e7jriic@google.com
CREATED:20150709T214209Z
DESCRIPTION:Directions\n160 Bleecker Street is where the pad is! Just ask t
 he doorman for the keys to APT #6AW.\nHouse Manual\nWhen you arrive\, tell 
 the doorman:\nHi my name is (your name) my friends left me the keys for the
 ir apartment\, 6AW.\nAfter getting keys\, go to the right of the stairs to 
 the elevator\, take elevator to the 6th floor. Exit elevator\, go left to t
 he atrium\, make a left and it will be the first apartment.\nPlease do not 
 mention AirBnB to anyone in the building. If anyone asks\, or the doorman a
 sks\, just say that you are our friends visiting NYC for the weekend. (NYC 
 is strict with AirBnB and landlords as well\, everyone in NYC has to take t
 hese precautions with AirBnB.)\nPLEASE DO NOT LEAVE THE KEYS INSIDE! DOOR W
 ILL LOCK WHEN SHUT. DO NOT LOSE THE KEY!!!!\nDo NOT use the light switch ab
 ove the couch\, that is for the power to the apartment.\nThe main kitchen l
 ight switch is behind the door from the foyer to the living area. Behind th
 e door you will also find the thermostat.\nInternet: \nWiFi Network: Barnab
 y's Stronghold \nWiFi Password: abc123abc1\nCoffee: \nNespresso Pods are un
 der the Nespresso Machine. (Setting is set to Lungo as default)\nTV: \nHDMI
  2 - Amazon FireTV \nHDMI 3 - PS3 \nHDMI 4 - TV \nPlease feel free to play 
 any PS3 games or watch any of the movies either via FireTV or BluRays!\nPle
 ase feel free to eat some of our food. Just leave us some when we come back
  hungry! :)\nSupplies for minor cleanups are under the sink\, as is the tra
 sh can and extra trash bags. Trash chute is out the door\, through Door C\,
  first door on left.\nAt the end of your stay\, unless notified otherwise p
 lease leave the key on the counter in the kitchen.\nMost important: Enjoy t
 he city!
LAST-MODIFIED:20150709T214209Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:AirBnB directions
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
