DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20160319
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20160320
DTSTAMP:20260409T144146Z
UID:3b3hcu4mppjrcacquh0g5lsrgs@google.com
CREATED:20160308T222657Z
DESCRIPTION:http://mntsutro.com/hiking/\nmailing to invite you to our next 
 Stitch Fix hike on Saturday March 19th at 11am. We'll be exploring Sutro Fo
 rest in San Francisco. \n\nPlease plan to meet at the forest entrance at St
 anyan and 17th in the Cole Valley neighborhood. The trailhead starts with a
  wooden staircase about two houses above the intersection. The area has 2 h
 our street parking - and it's near MUNI and several bus lines. Great pre or
  post hike brunch options at Zazie! But I digress... Hiking!\n\nI'd recomme
 nd dressing in layers. Because this area is heavily shaded\, and the west s
 ide of the tower can be pretty foggy\, it's usually long pant/light jacket 
 weather for me\, but you might break a sweat on the hill! We'll plan for ab
 out 2 hours of hiking\, with plenty of opportunities for folks to rest or t
 urn around if they're short on time. \n\nPartners\, kids and friends are we
 lcome! Dogs are allowed but they are supposed to be on leash at all times. 
 \n\nContact me with questions or if you're running late: 415-845-6578. We'l
 l wait until 11:15 and then get started!
LAST-MODIFIED:20160309T061214Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:stitch fix hike?
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
