UID:mi8visahqsfmo6ahqbot9294d0@google.com
CREATED:20170417T171458Z
DESCRIPTION:1:50PM - Gather downstairs and walk to Pier 40 (Townsend and Em
 barcadero)\n\n2:15-5:30 - Sailing lesson and team building with Captain Kir
 k\nThere will be sandwiches\, snacks\, and drinks (alcoholic and non-alcoho
 lic) on the boat\n\nPlease wear soft-soled shoes such as tennis shoes\; no 
 heels or cowboy boots. At times it can get cool on the bay\, so we recommen
 d long pants\, long sleeves\, a sweatshirt and a windbreaker just in case. 
 For winter or evening trips dress extra warmly.\n\n6PM (or whenever we get 
 there)- Dinner @ Americano (Hotel Vitale\, 8 Mission St\, San Francisco\, C
 A 94105)\n\nPlease make a note if you plan to not come to dinner. \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170417T171458Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ads R&D SF Offsite
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
