DESCRIPTION:(415) 772-0922\nAt Trestle\, we remember a time\, not too long 
 ago\, where people took pause to enjoy a meal in the presence of great comp
 any\, giving it the reverence and respect deserved.   We provide a dining e
 xperience served in courses\, with the satisfaction and warmth found at a f
 amily gathering\, creating the foundation to a proper meal. <br />Every nig
 ht we feature a changing 3 course pre fixe menu with choices on each course
  for $35/person. We will have an optional additional pasta course for $10/p
 erson. <br><br /><br />Our menu is posted nightly by midnight for the follo
 wing day. View the menu at www.trestlesf.com<br /><br />We are able to acco
 mmodate vegetarian options nightly. We do our best to accommodate other all
 ergies/restrictions based on the menu for that evening. <br />
