DESCRIPTION:Whether or not you're making your pilgrimage back to the playa 
 this year\, this is not one to miss. We're joining forces with the fantasti
 cal Camp Charlie for a sunrise filled with costumed characters\, loving vib
 es\, and morning mischief. We're being blessed by the voices of spoken word
  poet Eli Marienthal and singer Aleksandra Dubov\, and hitting up a new spo
 t\, SF's beloved cross-cultural community art space: SOMArts. As always\, d
 elicious coffee\, Organic Valley drinks\, KIND snacks\, and other goodies a
 re on the house. See you on the dance floor in your finest (and for some\, 
 dustiest) playa chic attire.  Questions? Send us a note at SF@dybrkr.com.  
 See you on the dance floor!\n\nJoin with Google Hangouts: https://hangouts.
 google.com/hangouts/_/radiant.sh/aaron?hceid=bjNqbXY2cXZhOW5sOWl2a2gwaWxlc2
 RsZm9AZ3JvdXAuY2FsZW5kYXIuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbQ.eg8r9h402nn023nr4dj90clevg&hs=121
LAST-MODIFIED:20150909T180147Z
LOCATION:SOMArts Cultural Center 934 Brannan Street San Francisco CA 94103
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:DAYBREAKER
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
