 \, press the word Schlage.\n\nCheck out the house manual for important info
  including wifi details and nearby recommendations. Please be sure to fill 
 out the Guest Registration card you'll find with the manual. The City of Po
 rtland REQUIRES that we retain these.\n\nIf you have any questions\, call o
 r text us at (503 951 8674). Have fun!
