UID:867876B9-256C-48C3-9931-6F3CE54ECAC9
CREATED:20180427T214056Z
DESCRIPTION:Hi friends\,\n\nIn (slightly belated) celebration of my last bi
 rthday before entering the next decade\, I would love to see you all and en
 joy some drinks and hopefully pleasant spring weather.  If you're free\, pl
 ease come join me (and the new baby bird that just hatched in a flower pot 
 on my balcony).\n\nFriday May 4th \n5:30pm onwards\n587 Vermont St \n\nNo o
 rnaments required for entry\, but I would welcome any contributions in the 
 alcohol and/or food departments.  As it is May-the-Fourth-be-with-you day\,
  Star Wars-themed anything is definitely not discouraged.  \n\nHope to see 
 you there!\n-Jessie 
LAST-MODIFIED:20180427T214056Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Jessi Carr party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
