DESCRIPTION:Lockbox instructions\nAt the South East corner of Portland Stre
 et and Wellington Street (across the street from the building and at the st
 reet corner next to the Bike Share docking station) there is a telephone/po
 wer pole. At the bottom of the yellow plastic anchor attached to the pole i
 s a Lock Box or 'key-safe'. It is Silver and is the one facing the park. Th
 e code for the lockbox is 0985. Inside you will find a key and fob (to acce
 ss the building). Please make sure to close and lock the lockbox and scramb
 le the code after removing the key. Also\, this is where you will leave the
  keys on checkout.
LAST-MODIFIED:20170627T171327Z
LOCATION:508 Wellington Street West Apt 305 Toronto\, ON M5V 1E3 Canada
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:AirBnb after 3pm check in
TRANSP:OPAQUE
