DESCRIPTION:Jeep Safari for 2 adults\n\nTel: 30 210 9244345\n\nConfirmation
  No: 206607\n\nNot Included:- \n• Hotel pick up • Lunch\n\nDURATION 8 hours
 \n\nDEPARTSMonday\, Wednesday and Thursday at 9:30am\n\nTOUR ITINERARY\nExp
 lore the island of Mykonos on our off-road safari. You see the north side\,
  the light house\, the higher regions\, the water reservoir lake\, the area
  around Ano Mera with the women's monastery and the old Venetian fortress P
 aleokastro\, you explore the east side with great views and a deserted mine
 \, where the ground is full of interesting minerals.Enjoy lunch (not includ
 ed in price) by the sea in one of the gorgeous bays before driving to the s
 outh with its great beaches where we have a swim stop. At the last stop abo
 ve Mykonos town you can take a wonderful panoramic picture for a memory of 
 an unforgettable day
LAST-MODIFIED:20180717T154957Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Jeep Safari Tour
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
