CREATED:20171212T180217Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>hi friends!<br><br><br>as you have heard\, our time in the 
 mission has come to an end. our landlord is selling our apartment for north
  of $1 million and so we must go. we\, the gentrifiers\, have literally bee
 n forced out by gentrification. #sanfrancisco<br><br>we're so sad to leave\
 , but thrilled to have found an amazing new place in rockridge! before we f
 orce you to come to oakland for our next housewarming (it's nice over there
 \, we promise!)\, we must first say goodbye this apartment. hence: a housec
 ooling!<br><br><b>what:&nbsp\;</b>saying goodbye to our san francisco apart
 ment and emotionally preparing yourself to come visit us in oakland<br><b>w
 hen:&nbsp\;</b><span tabindex="0">saturday 12/16 8 pm</span>-bedtime<br><b>
 where:&nbsp\;</b><a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=3436+18th+street\,+sf\
 ,+ca+94110&amp\;entry=gmail&amp\;source=g">3436 18th street\, sf\, ca 94110
 </a><br><br>we'll rustle up some festive drinks and snacks. if you'd like t
 o bring anything\, more drinks and snacks would be wonderful. if it gets to
 o crowded (read: if we are simply too popular)\, we shall decamp to wildhaw
 k\, conveniently located one block away.<br><br>let us know if you can come
  -- excited to hopefully see you&nbsp\;<span tabindex="0">on saturday</span
 >!<br><br>love\,<br>julie and nick
LAST-MODIFIED:20171212T180231Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Julie + Nick Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
