DESCRIPTION:Phone: 844-421-0804\n\n\nYour COVID-19 vaccination appointment 
 is at 1034 Oak Grove Rd.\, Concord\, \nCA 94518. Additional parking is avai
 lable on Fox Way if needed.\n\n\n\nThere is a 15-30 minute observation peri
 od after the vaccine is \nadministered.\n\n\n\nPlease bring your insurance 
 card to your appointment. There is no cost to \nyou for this appointment. \
 n\n\n\nAll three vaccines are safe and highly effective against COVID. If y
 ou \nchoose Johnson & Johnson (Janssen)\, you will automatically be schedul
 ed \nfor a booster dose 2 months later. If you choose Pfizer or Moderna\, a
  \nsecond-dose appointment will automatically be scheduled for you 3-4 week
 s \nafter you get your first shot.\n\n\n\nIf you are positive for COVID\, e
 xperiencing symptoms\, or have had close \ncontact with someone with COVID\
 , DO NOT get your vaccine or booster shot \nnow. You should wait until your
  isolation or quarantine is over\, and your \nsymptoms resolve.\n\n\n\nIf y
 ou have already received a COVID-19 vaccination\, please bring your CDC \nV
 accination card with you to this appointment.\n\n\n\nMinors getting vaccina
 ted should be accompanied by an adult caretaker or \nhave written consent f
 rom a parent or legal guardian.\n\n\n\nThank you and have a great day!\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20220915T212144Z
LOCATION:1034 Oak Grove Rd\, Concord CA 94518
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:COVID-19 Vaccine Dose
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
