 ow. No cheating! (Scouts honor)<br><a href="https://forms.gle/zVkA2QeVuHMFD
 fNo9" target="_blank">Answer Sheet</a>  PS: This sheet get&#39\;s re-used f
 or every round. <br><br>Round 3 will be a music round!<br><br>Teams are all
