UID:108qev78dn9haaduud2d2ribnf@google.com
CREATED:20220515T185354Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>Instructions:<br></b>1. Sign up for a date - we're aiming fo
 r every other day starting May 16th (not grayed out). If you absolutely nee
 d a day in gray\, no worries!<br><br>2. If you are doing food delivery\, ai
 m for 5:30/6PM on that date\, and in the instructions\, please use:    Addr
 ess: 2773 Folsom St\, #202\; San Francisco\, CA 94110    Nick's phone numbe
 r: 214-673-4274    Instructions of 'Please ring the doorbell for Apt #202' 
 to place the order<br><br>3. If you are delivering food yourself and want t
 o say hello\, Julie and/or Nick would love to say hello outside with masks 
 on -- you can generally aim for the same 5:30/6PM PDT or after timeframe si
 nce it will be dependent on work schedule\, but feel free to text Nick lead
 ing up to the time to double-check.<br><b><br>4. Food ordering/making consi
 derations: Please look for gluten-free meals (some amount of gluten\, e.g. 
 soy sauce\, is okay\; Nick can eat wheat -- just not a big bowl of pasta)<b
 r></b><br>5. If a giftcard is more your style\, DoorDash is much preferred!
LAST-MODIFIED:20220516T173852Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Order Food Delivery for Nick and Julie
TRANSP:OPAQUE
