CREATED:20230911T232840Z
DESCRIPTION:Sharing” (show and tell) starts in October\, the children take 
 turns sharing according to their assigned day each month\, the sharing cale
 ndar will be posted in the Patter each month\, the day of the week that you
 r child will have sharing can change due to holidays etc. We use sharing as
  a language building activity during our small group circle times. Our goal
  is to build confidence in public speaking and to practice listening skills
  for their classmates. Your child can choose 1 item\, children often enjoy 
 showing a favorite toy\, book\, photo or nature item. The item is to remain
  in the child’s cubby for the rest of the school day.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230911T232849Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Leo Sharing Day!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
