DTSTART:20240201T074500Z
DTEND:20240201T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T144146Z
UID:2smoqcel4r31cvrg8knaq6hr40@google.com
CREATED:20240131T205538Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Dewing Park Swim Club and Team registration opens February 1
 st at midnight (so tonight!). <strong>Sea Ponies filled up very quickly las
 t year</strong>\, so if you are interested in Sea Ponies I would recommend 
 signing up tonight. All other registration can probably wait till the morni
 ng. smiley Reminder that all Swim Team families\, (except families with onl
 y 15/18 swimmers) must be pool members and until registration to the pool i
 s complete\, their swimmer is not officially on the team. Sea Ponies must b
 e members as well or first time famiies must pay a Splash Fee Guest Members
 hip.  </p><p> <span> <span> <span> Registration for the pool closes March 3
 1. <u>A late fee of $50 will be assessed after this date and we cannot guar
 antee membership</u>. New memberships are limited but will continue to be a
 vailable until they run out.</span></span></span> </p><p>   </p><p> <span> 
 <span> <span> To register for the pool go to: </span></span></span><a href=
 "https://www.dewingparkswimclub.com/fees">https://www.<wbr />dewingparkswim
 club.com/fees</a> and <strong>click on the  Club Registration box</strong>.
   </p><p>   </p><p> A general membership meeting will take place in March. 
 Stay tuned for the date and zoom link. At the meeting we will vote on incre
 asing the number of Splash-Fee guest membership available in our by-lawys. 
 New this year\, all Sea Ponies have to be members or pay a new family Splas
 h Fee so we need additional Splash Fee guest memberships available.    <br>
  <br> </p>     <ul><li> <p> <span> <span><b> Annual Membership</b></span>: 
 $725</span> </p>       <ul><li> <p> <span> Dues for returning members in go
 od standing. Does not include a maintenance fee ($150)\, which can be refun
 ded with four hours of volunteer work.</span> </p></li><li> <p> <span> Note
 : A one-time Buy-In Fee ($650) will be applied when families join as member
 -owners\, their first year or after a Rental year.</span> </p></li></ul> </
 li></ul>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240131T205538Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Dewing Park Pool Sign up!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
