DTSTAMP:20260409T144146Z
UID:42stdl5fa76nk1dit23thhgkj3@google.com
CREATED:20240423T022118Z
DESCRIPTION:KIDS LIKE TRUCKS! AND KIDS LOVE BIG TRUCKS!\nThe Rotary Club of
  Lafayette\, CA is planning the first ever KEEP ON TRUCKIN' family\nfun eve
 nt on Sunday\, April 28\, 2024. The event will bring together trucks of all
  kinds to one place where kids can have “hands-on” experience to see\, touc
 h and meet the men and women who operate these vehicles. The event will als
 o feature additional family\nactivities\, food & beverages and a chance to 
 meet some of our local first responders.\nIncluded in the collection of tru
 cks will be Garbage Trucks\, Street Sweeper\, Dump Trucks\, Tow Trucks\, Ch
 erry Pickers\, Fire Trucks\, Police vehicles and a Command Center\, Cement 
 Truck\, and a few surprises too.\nKeep on Truckin'\nSaturday April 27th\, 2
 024\n9:00am - 1:00pm\nQuiet Hour 12:00pm -1:00pm\nCity of Lafayette - Golde
 n Gate Way (Mt. Diablo Blvd. - 1st Street)\nSmall entrance fee for attendee
 s. All proceeds to benefit Shelter\, Inc. \nSee less
LAST-MODIFIED:20240423T022118Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Keep On Trucking
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
