DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Monday\, November 24th | 2–9pm</strong><br><strong>M
 endocino Farms –</strong><strong> </strong><strong><a href="https://www.goo
 gle.com/maps/dir//Mendocino+Farms\,+1895+Ygnacio+Valley+Rd+%2328\,+Walnut+C
 reek\,+CA+94598/@37.919029\,-122.1197549\,12z/data=!4m8!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0
 x8085618a0da3ca61:0x104336fabee56375!2m2!1d-122.0373532!2d37.9189223?entry=
 ttu&amp\;g_ep=EgoyMDI1MTAyOS4yIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" target="_blank">1895 Yg
 nacio Valley Rd #28 Walnut Creek\, CA 94598</a></strong></p><p>Take a break
  from holiday cooking and support Pied Piper Preschool! To participate\, sh
 ow the attached event flyer at the register <strong>or</strong> order onlin
 e at <a href="https://www.mendocinofarms.com/" target="_blank">mendocinofar
 ms.com</a> using code <strong>GIVEBACK. </strong>Pied Piper Preschool will 
 receive<em> </em><strong><strong>30% of the sales from our group.</strong><
 /strong></p><p>Invite your <strong>friends\, family\, and coworkers</strong
 > to join in and help raise funds for Pied Piper while enjoying something d
 elicious!</p>
